{"problem": "Compute\n\\[\\cos \\frac{2 \\pi}{7} \\cos \\frac{4 \\pi}{7} \\cos \\frac{8 \\pi}{7}.\\]", "level": "Level 2", "type": "Precalculus", "solution": "Let $x = \\cos \\frac{2 \\pi}{7} \\cos \\frac{4 \\pi}{7} \\cos \\frac{8 \\pi}{7}.$  Then by repeated application of the double angle formula,\n\\begin{align*}\nx \\sin \\frac{2 \\pi}{7} &= \\sin \\frac{2 \\pi}{7} \\cos \\frac{2 \\pi}{7} \\cos \\frac{4 \\pi}{7} \\cos \\frac{8 \\pi}{7} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{2} \\sin \\frac{4 \\pi}{7} \\cos \\frac{4 \\pi}{7} \\cos \\frac{8 \\pi}{7} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{4} \\cos \\frac{8 \\pi}{7} \\cos \\frac{8 \\pi}{7} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\sin \\frac{16 \\pi}{7} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\sin \\frac{2 \\pi}{7},\n\\end{align*}so $x = \\boxed{\\frac{1}{8}}.$", "wolframquery": "Query: cos(2pi/7)*cos(4pi/7)*cos(8pi/7)", "wolframoutput": "Wolfram Alpha could not find an answer and encountered an error.", "gptanswer": "Let $z = e^{2 \\pi i/7}.$  Then $z^7 = 1,$ so $z^6 + z^5 + z^4 + z^3 + z^2 + z + 1 = 0.$  Then\n\\[(z - 1)(z^6 + z^5 + z^4 + z^3 + z^2 + z + 1) = z^7 - 1 = 0,\\]so $z^6 + z^5 + z^4 + z^3 + z^2 + z + 1 = 0.$\n\nNote that\n\\begin{align*}\n\\cos \\frac{2 \\pi}{7} + \\cos \\frac{4 \\pi}{7} + \\cos \\frac{8 \\pi}{7} &= \\operatorname{Re} (z + z^2 + z^4) \\\\\n&= \\operatorname{Re} \\frac{z^7 - z}{z - 1} \\\\\n&= \\operatorname{Re} \\frac{-z}{z - 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{2}.\n\\end{align*}Then\n\\begin{align*}\n\\cos \\frac{2 \\pi}{7} \\cos \\frac{4 \\pi}{7} \\cos \\frac{8 \\pi}{7} &= \\frac{1}{8} (2 \\cos \\frac{2 \\pi}{7}) (2 \\cos \\frac{4 \\pi}{7}) (2 \\cos \\frac{8 \\pi}{7}) \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} (z + \\frac{1}{z}) (z^2 + \\frac{1}{z^2}) (z^4 + \\frac{1}{z^4}) \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^2 + 1)(z^4 + z^2 + 1)(z^8 + z^4 + 1)}{z^7} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^2 + 1)(z^4 + z^2 + 1)(z^6 - 1)}{z^6} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^2 + 1)(z^4 + z^2 + 1)(-z - z^2 - z^3 - z^4 - z^5 - z^6)}{z^6 + z^5 + z^4 + z^3 + z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^2 + 1)(z^4 + z^2 + 1)(-z - z^2 - z^3 + z^2 + z + 1)}{-z^2 - z - 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^2 + 1)(z^4 + z^2 + 1)(-z^3 + 1)}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^2 + 1)(z^4 + z^2 + 1)(z^3 + 1)}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^6 + z^4 + z^2 + 1)(z^3 + 1)}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^6 + z^4 + z^2 + 1)(z^3 + 1)(z - 1)}{z^3 - 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^7 - z)(z^6 + z^4 + z^2 + 1)(z^3 + 1)(z - 1)}{(z - 1)(z^2 + z + 1)(z^3 - 1)} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^6 - 1)(z^6 + z^4 + z^2 + 1)(z^3 + 1)}{(z - 1)(z^2 + z + 1)(z - 1)(z^2 - z + 1)(z + 1)} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^6 + z^4 + z^2 + 1)(z^3 + 1)}{(z^2 + z + 1)(z^2 - z + 1)(z + 1)} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^6 + z^4 + z^2 + 1)(z^3 + 1)}{(z^2 + z + 1)(z^2 + z + 1)(z - 1)} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^6 + z^4 + z^2 + 1)(z^3 + 1)}{(z^2 + z + 1)^2(z - 1)} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^6 + z^4 + z^2 + 1)(z^3 + 1)}{(z^2 + z + 1)^2(z^3 + 1)} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{z^6 + z^4 + z^2 + 1}{(z^2 + z + 1)^2} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^6 - z^5 + z^5 - z^4 + z^4 - z^3 + z^3 - z^2 + z^2 - z + 1)}{(z^2 + z + 1)^2} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{z^5 - z^4 + z^3 - z^2 + z - 1}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{(z^5 + z^4 + z^3 + z^2 + z + 1) - 2z^4 - 2z^2 + 2}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{-2z^4 - 2z^2 + 2}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{-2(z^2 + 1)z^2}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{-2(z^2 + z + 1 - z - 1)z^2}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{-2(z^2 + z + 1)z^2 + 2z^2}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{-2(z^4 + z^2 + 1) + 2z^2}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{-2(z^4 + z^2 + 1) + 2(z^2 + z + 1) - 2z - 2}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{-2z^4 - 2z^3 + 2z - 2}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{-2(z^3 + z^2 - z - 1)}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{-2(z - 1)(z^2 + 2z + 1)}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{-2(z - 1)(z + 1)^2}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{-2(z - 1)(z - \\omega)(z - \\omega^2)(z + 1)}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot \\frac{-2(z^2 - z + 1)(z^2 + z + 1)}{z^2 + z + 1} \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{8} \\cdot (-2z^2 + 2) \\\\\n&= \\boxed{\\frac{1}{2}}.\n\\end{align*}", "boxed": "boxed"}